reviews_data.review_text:
Store was clean, spacious, bright. The woman working the counter was on her elbows, had her head down. I mentioned it was my first time visiting, got no help as to what may be good in the menu or what I may like. Your standard coffee spot, and I knew I liked caribou already so fine I got this vanilla cold mess...they don't have regular cold foam she tells me...the drink was supposed to be a splash of milk...it's totally white....I drank the entirety of the drink in I kid you not, 6 slurps. Gone. It was ALL ICE and milk. They did add whip cream for me but for $7 I'm not coming back. Please stand at the register and don't talk to the menu, turn and face the customer so we can hear you. You clearly saw I had hospital bandages on and a bracelet, and that I didn't feel well, and want to act a certain way when I can't hear you? And this is who you have training the new people?

Absolutely not never coming back
reviews_data.owner_answer: We are sorry to hear you didn't have a great experience at our store. Can you email us at customerrelations@cariboucoffee.com so we can follow up with you? Please provide your Caribou Perks account information if you're a member. Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text: Got my free rewards for using app. So easy to order and pay. So far have loved everything I've ordered iced drinks, egg,   cheese, bacon sandwiches yummy.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for letting us know you enjoyed your visit. We hope to welcome you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Best coffee in Monroe
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for letting us know you had a great time. Looking forward to your next visit!

reviews_data.review_text: This place won’t last long with ridiculous prices they’re charging. 7.50 for one coffee ! Double cost of dunkin for an inferior product .
reviews_data.owner_answer: We are sorry to hear you didn't have a great experience at our store. Can you email us at customerrelations@cariboucoffee.com so we can follow up with you? Please provide your Caribou Perks account information if you're a member. Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text: Loved my first visit to Caribou Coffee Monroe! Tried the combo and it was delicious. My cold press was amazing and the Lumberjack breakfast sandwich was fresh, hot and tasty! Definitely coming back!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for letting us know you enjoyed your visit. We hope to welcome you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text:
First time ever coming to Caribou Coffee and it will not be our last! David helped us at the drive through and he made the visit so worth it. I love it when the employees enjoy their job and David seemed to enjoy his! He was very helpful, personable, and he gave us a card to sign up for the app which I did as soon as I got home.

I’m very particular about my coffee and Caribou met the standard! So delicious. I will definitely be back to order more items off of the menu.
reviews_data.owner_answer: We're glad to hear you enjoyed your visit. Come back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Dark coffee of the day was good.
reviews_data.owner_answer: We appreciate you sharing your positive experience. Hope to have you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Had a great visit this morning at Caribou. Employees are very friendly and service was quick.

reviews_data.review_text: Waited in the drive thru line for 25 minutes, literally, but will chalk it up to being newly opened. The breakfast biscuit was amazing. Wife and daughter love the coffee (not a drinker myself). Will return.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for letting us know you enjoyed your visit. We hope to welcome you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text:
First time trying Caribou and loved it! I got the Blended Caramel High Rise and the Turkey Provolone Asiago Bagel. Loved
my drink and my bagel was SO good!! Definitely will be going back!
reviews_data.owner_answer: We appreciate you sharing your positive experience. Hope to have you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text:
This location opened on Friday May 2, 2024 and is the first location in the Monroe area. This was my first time trying caribou coffee and the experience was great.

We got a nitro high rise and a vanilla shaken espresso with oat milk. For our food we got a chorizo breakfast burrito and a bacon egg and cheese bagel. The food portions were significantly more than Starbucks as well.

The staff was friendly and knowledgeable about what caribou offers and the store was tidy and clean apart from boxed supplies being stored by our table which is no big deal.

I would definitely come here again!
